===Etymology===
From {{AGr.}} '''[[ήλεκτρον]]''' (''elektron'') "amber", from prefix '''[[έλ-]]''' (''el-'') "sun, bright, shiny".
See also ''[[electric]]'' + ''[[-on]]''.

